Package: flashcard
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight cross-platform flashcard application
 Flashcard is a minimal yet feature-rich flashcard GUI application
 built with C and Raylib. Supports CSV data format for easy management
 and provides a clean, distraction-free learning interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Cross-platform (Linux/Windows)
  - CSV-based card storage with escape sequence support
  - Catppuccin Mocha color scheme
  - Score tracking and shuffle modes
  - Minimal dependencies (Raylib only)
